{"tid":1694693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺大廈大堂痴文宣 保安疑似報警 可以點做？","createTime":"2019-11-05T09:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:10:26.000Z","uid":59066,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"30a47d2f004029346f0618935a807c414ff5ac51","tid":1694693,"uid":59066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"自己嗰區頗藍 特別自己住嗰幢大廈<br />\n個大廈業主立案法團腐敗兼極親民建聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近區議會選舉臨近<br />\n大堂張民建聯poster極傷眼<br />\n上星期我痴咗張不投奶共政黨嘅文宣上去<br />\n唔想教化班深藍 但想啲中立游離分子<br />\n可以考慮清楚 好好運用手上面嗰一票<br />\n難得有多個人參選<br />\n唔好再俾民建聯個垃圾區議員自動當選<br />\n之後幾日都聽到大廈啲藍絲嘅閒言閒語<br />\n趁我出入講話咩報警嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n今日見到佢哋揾人備份咗我貼文宣嘅閉路電視<br />\n我估佢哋應該想有進一步行動<br />\n<br />\n我做得都唔怕認 閉路電視亦有record<br />\n只係想知有冇咩我需要知等我做好心理準備<br />\n例如要罰千五嗰啲？<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港人 反抗"},{"pid":"9150b4ec07cb7d72ce86b0985822cfe1bd05af9e","tid":1694693,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"執屋先？"},{"pid":"656a1546ec2b19f856366c52fd333aeeb1a32f36","tid":1694693,"uid":310858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"清野先"},{"pid":"74cab5febf94732be5ec0237460a716b9f6e37ba","tid":1694693,"uid":320293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"即刻屌到個保安冇聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47d7a56cc8ce3ad843d796df0b812dffa7b91ad","tid":1694693,"uid":59066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9150b4ec07cb7d72ce86b0985822cfe1bd05af9e","tid":1694693,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"執屋先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T09:15:12.000Z","msg":"知道"},{"pid":"3005ee771a9a53ec4a46e6de41b47b0426ca0f8f","tid":1694693,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"係大廈貼野可